        {{!-- Overview Tab --}}
        <div class="tab active" data-tab="overview">
            <h2><i class="fa-solid fa-dice-d20"></i> Tavern Twenty-One</h2>
            <p class="subtitle">A game of Fortune, Folly, and reckless abandon.</p>

            <div class="help-card">
                <h3><i class="fa-solid fa-bullseye"></i> The Goal</h3>
                <p>
                    Reach a <strong>Total of 21</strong> (or close to it) without going over ("Busting").<br>
                    The highest total wins the pot. Ties are settled by a <strong>Duel</strong>.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="help-card">
                <h3><i class="fa-solid fa-forward"></i> Game Flow</h3>
                <ol class="help-list">
                    <li><strong>Ante Up:</strong> Everyone pays the toll.</li>
                    <li><strong>The Opening:</strong> Roll 2d10 (One visible, one hidden).</li>
                    <li><strong>The Cut:</strong> Lowest visible die may re-roll their hole die.</li>
                    <li><strong>Betting:</strong> Take turns buying dice, holding, or using skills.</li>
                    <li><strong>Showdown:</strong> All dice revealed. Accusations are made.</li>
                    <li><strong>Payout:</strong> Winner takes all.</li>
                </ol>
            </div>

            <div class="help-card">
                <h3><i class="fa-solid fa-coins"></i> Betting & Actions</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Hit (Buy Die):</strong> Add a d4, d6, d8, d10, or d20 to your total.</li>
                    <li><strong>Hold:</strong> Compete with your current total.</li>
                    <li><strong>Fold:</strong> Leave the round (Refund 50% Ante if early).</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

