                    <div class="skill-body">
                        <p>Physically disrupt the table.</p>
                        <hr>
                        <ul>
                            <li><strong>Success:</strong> Re-roll Target's die.</li>
                            <li><strong>Fail:</strong> Target re-rolls YOUR die.</li>
                            <li><strong>Nat 1:</strong> Fail + Pay Ante.</li>
