        {{!-- Goblin Rules Tab --}}
        <div class="tab" data-tab="goblin">
            <h2><i class="fa-solid fa-skull"></i> Goblin Rules (Russian Roulette)</h2>
            <p class="subtitle">Fast. Brutal. No skills, no accusations, no staredown.</p>

            <div class="help-card">
                <h3><i class="fa-solid fa-dice"></i> Core Rules</h3>
                <ul class="help-list">
                    <li><strong>Start at 0:</strong> No opening hand, no cut.</li>
                    <li><strong>Roll once per die:</strong> d20, d10, d8, d6, d4 (one each).</li>
                    <li><strong>Coin is unlimited:</strong> Flip as many times as you dare.</li>
                    <li><strong>Nat 1 = Bust:</strong> Any die or coin tail ends you.</li>
                    <li><strong>d20 Nat 20:</strong> Explodes and can be rolled again.</li>
                    <li><strong>Highest total wins:</strong> No 21 cap.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="help-card">
                <h3><i class="fa-solid fa-coins"></i> Coin Flip</h3>
                <ul class="help-list">
                    <li><strong>Heads (2):</strong> Double your total.</li>
                    <li><strong>Tails (1):</strong> Immediate bust.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="help-card">
                <h3><i class="fa-solid fa-ban"></i> Disabled</h3>
                <ul class="help-list">
                    <li><strong>Skills:</strong> All skills are disabled.</li>
                    <li><strong>Accusations:</strong> Disabled.</li>
                    <li><strong>Staredown:</strong> Skipped.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
